<plot>Once Upon A Christmas Dream is a new family Christmas film bringing the imagination of two young kids to life; "A simple Christmas wish is this season's magical family gift." Joanna Johnson is a hardworking parent of two beloved children, Krista Johnson and Christian Johnson, trying to fill a gap in her family's life. Since the death of her husband, Joanna tries to write the next big story in hopes of succeeding to a better life for herself and her children. When one night Krista and Christian slumber into a magical artifact filled with imaginative journeys, they begin a quest through the world of Christmas to find jolly ole Saint Nick and to only discover the imagination of a world created around the special adventures from two kids' vision of Christmas. Approaching the end of their journey, they meet Santa Claus, who expresses his appreciation of the letter he was sent of their Christmas wish. Santa begins to send the kids back to the world they came from where they awake on Christmas day to a magical surprise for their mother and the story she was searching for.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?411620</url></doc>
